nodes.text: The Jabiim system was a star system located within the Phelleem sector in the Outer Rim region of the galaxy which contained the planet Jabiim and the cognominal star.
During the Cold War between the Galactic Republic and the Sith Empire, the Jabiim system was the theater of a battle concluded with a Sith victory.
